  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218900/extras/f6d37dcd5427d5c3c651358f6ad7fa16.avif?t=1727089364\" width=500 height=166 /></span><br><br>Minimal physical puzzle with explosions. The player's goal to keep the blue ball on the platform for 3 seconds in order to pass the level.<br><br>Zup! Z - the continuation of the franchise<br><br>▪ 60 Levels<br>▪ Achievements<br>▪ New cubes<br>▪ Lasers<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trading Cards</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218900/extras/75e14a69304c52f76953153e48241fef.avif?t=1727089364\" width=498 height=347 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Emoticons</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1218900/extras/fc387f017f4945d65bd2833d751594b7.avif?t=1727089364\" width=233 height=120 /></span></h2><br>Requires DirectShow to work correctly (K-Lite Codec Pack)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Credits</strong></h2>\"Zup!\" powered by Clickteam Fusion 2.5<br><br>The basis is taken an example of Sergio Andre</h2>",
